[19/02/2018 23:15:54] <font color="#ffffff">Esa voz...</font>
[19/02/2018 23:15:57] <font color="#ffffff">(Isaac!</font>
[19/02/2018 23:16:02] <font color="#ffffff">Angustias.</font>
